<h1> Youngest director </h1>

<% @youngest_director = Director.all.order({ :dob => :desc }).at(0) %>

<p>
  The youngest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= @youngest_director.id %>"> <%= @youngest_director.name %></a>, born on <%= @youngest_director.dob.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %>.
</p>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>

